OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cool start but largely dry
OL,6,Fwith partly cloudy skies, clearing to
OL,7,Fsunny spells. Turning cloudier during
OL,8,Fthe afternoon with sunny intervals
OL,9,Fbecoming limited to coasts. Breezy,
OL,10,Fwinds easing later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FPartly cloudy skies and some
OL,13,Fsunny intervals this evening. Cloud
OL,14,Fincreasing from the north overnight
OL,15,Fwith showery rain toward the end of
OL,16,Fthe night. Becoming breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
