OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FAny early cloud and rain
OL,6,Fclearing, then largely dry and bright
OL,7,Fwith sunny intervals and a few coastal
OL,8,Fshowers. Breezy, though strong winds
OL,9,Fnear coasts.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBreezy
OL,12,Fand cloudy, with outbreaks of rain
OL,13,FTuesday, followed by showers. Blustery
OL,14,Fshowers, with possible thunder, and
OL,15,Fsome sunny intervals Wednesday and
OL,16,FThursday. Cool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
